Author: Philip Haynes <Philip.haynes@me.com>
Date:   Tue Jul 7 18:37:17 2026 +1000

    feat(QuantumInfo): prove qRelativeEnt_joint_convexity (joint convexity of Umegaki relative entropy)
    
    Closes the sorry in QuantumInfo/Entropy/Relative.lean by proving joint convexity of the
    Umegaki quantum relative entropy from the already-proved sandwiched-Renyi joint convexity
    (alpha->1). Placed in DPI.lean (which imports Relative.lean) to reach that machinery
    without an import cycle. Supporting API: qRelativeEnt_ne_top_iff/eq_top_iff (Relative.lean),
    Mixable.mix_one (Prob.lean), and private mixture/limit lemmas (DPI.lean). #print axioms:
    only propext/Classical.choice/Quot.sound.
    
    Signed-off-by: Philip Haynes <Philip.haynes@me.com>
    Co-authored-by: Helios <helios@helios.local>
    Co-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.8 <claude@helios.local>
    Co-authored-by: Codex gpt-5.5 <codex@helios.local>

